  "body": "Hello,\r\n\r\nI've noticed snapshot download is really slow and often speed drops to zero:\r\n\r\n```\r\nDec 18 12:09:42 polygon-archive-de-1 erigon[2387425]: [INFO] [12-18|12:09:42.258] [1/15 Snapshots] downloading (or verifying) progress=\"85.22% 755.4GB/886.4GB\" time-left=999hrs:99m total-time=3h15m40s download=0B/s upload=0B/s peers=58 files=991 connections=293 alloc=4.9GB sys=8.3GB\r\n```\r\n\r\nCan I help the network somehow and seed these torrents with a regular torrent client?",
