    "body": "Yes: \r\n```\r\nmake downloader\r\n./build/bin/downloader —seedbox —chain=bor-mainnet —datadir=<your> \r\n```\r\n\r\ncan use\r\n`—torrent.upload.rate=10m —torrent.download.rate=10m` to control speed\r\nIt supports `—nat` same as erigon. \r\n\r\nServer can be small and disk can be cheap. ",
